page.title: 20ABOUT THIS PROJECT.
page.content:
{ }We enjoyed this work and learned a great deal.We do not actually live in these areas,although we have friends and relations there and that made finding first-hand information difficult.Our area has been used as an overspill area from London and consequently does not have a definite personality and history yet.Where families have been settled for two or three generations, as in West Tilbury and in Chadwell there is more community spirit. { SUSAN DICKENSON JANE LIGGINS, { JOANNE QUINLAN, { TOBY MERRIMAN DAVID TAYLOR. {CHRISTINE HENDERSON
aided by{:MELANIE ANDERSON, { JACKIE CORPS, CHRISTIAN FEATHERSTONE, { STEVEN GILBODY and LI-AN HENDERSON.
